"{\"uid\": \"newsaf.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-05-Djokovic-beats-Alcaraz-to-win-Olympic-tennis-gold-1vNGYwEUD6M-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  Serbia's Novak Djokovic poses with his gold medal after defeating Spain's Carlos Alcaraz during the men's singles tennis final during the 2024 Summer Olympics, August 4, 2024, Paris, France. /CFP  Novak Djokovic beat Carlos Alcaraz on Sunday to claim a maiden Olympic title and become just the fifth player to complete a career Golden Slam.  (With input from AFP)  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"